{
  "texts": [
    "We contribute to the literature on the social dimensions and implications of LLMs through a comparative analysis of human-authored and AI-generated text.",
    "Specifically, we organize our work around the following research questions:",
    "How does the writing style of AI compare with the writing style of humans?",
    "Are there specific groups of people whose writing style is most closely imitated by AI? 2.",
    "What are the social characteristics of the humans whose essay is the most similar to a given AI generated essay? 3."
  ]
}